      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how much of a joke it all is. like we spend our whole lives struggling, working, feeling pain, just for the universe to eventually freeze and turn into nothing. in a billion years nothing we do matters. even our memories. it feels so pointless to even keep trying.",
