    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but why is it admirable? it's just biologically driven. we're programmed to keep going because instinct tells us to, but there's no actual reason to. if you really look at the math, the energy we spend just to exist is a waste. it's like trying to build a sandcastle while the tide is coming in. it's just irrational to keep building.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
